R3.pm examples

Copyright (c) 1999 Johan Schoen
The R3.pm examples are free software; you my use, modify and
redistribute them under the same terms as Perl itself.

You will most probably need to change the logon parameters
in each script for them to work on your system.

list_usr.pl:
List all users currently logged on to the same application server 
as the script.

popup.pl:
Sends a popup message to a logged on R/3 user.

ccbapi.pl
Displays company codes, using BAPI interface.



